episodes.title: My name is Ruth and I'm a cult survivor.
episodes.description:
My name is Ruth and I'm a cult survivor

I will say that Paul's mentors never meant for this group to be a cult, they simply wanted to teach people about God. Paul was like a son to them. Everything changed when Paul became leader. 

Thank you so much for listening and feel free to follow to hear more stories😊
